don't care.  Maybe he will make a good point, maybe he is being a jerk. It's probably both.  Candace?  I rarely listen to her, so Don't Care.  Does she even live in this country anymore?  It Doesn't Really Matter.  If Trump wants to go in and finally deal with some really bad characters--fine.  We'll see how it goes.  I assume no one actually has perfect insight except God Himself and God will be the ultimate judge of it.   But the strawman arguments I hear from the talking heads on our side need to just calm down. ", "author": "OldMule68", "created": 1773698594538, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "SisterCovfefeToo", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "It's just so exhausting.", "last_comment_created": 1773710438683, "content": "<p>Are you guys like me right now?  I am so done with the constant drama that comes with picking stupid &quot;sides&quot; that I don't care about.  Tucker?  Don't care.  If he is against a foreign war--I don't care.  Maybe he will make a good point, maybe he is being a jerk. It's probably both.  Candace?  I rarely listen to her, so Don't Care.  Does she even live in this country anymore?  It Doesn't Really Matter.  If Trump wants to go in and finally deal with some really bad characters--fine.  We'll see how it goes.  I assume no one actually has perfect insight except God Himself and God will be the ultimate judge of it.   But the strawman arguments I hear from the talking heads on our side need to just calm down.</p>\n", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 27, "score_up": 86, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_s